    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in good overall condition. It has been well-maintained, with the engine running smoothly and all major systems functioning as expected. The interior is clean, although there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor scuffs on the door panels. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, but you will notice a few small stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches from regular use. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner.",
