      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior is absolutely flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, chips, or scratches to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in like-new condition, with the original leather upholstery still firm and free of any wear or fading. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been maintained strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule with all records available. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that presents and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
