    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, and it really shows in every little detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without that full new-car price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
