    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a peerless E92 M3, featuring the S65B40 4.0L naturally aspirated V8\u2014a masterpiece of engineering with an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is in an impeccable state of preservation, showcasing a rigid chassis free of subframe fatigue. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The vehicle is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing precise compression and rebound settings for superior lateral dynamics. Critically, preventative maintenance has been performed, including treated rod bearing replacement and reinforced throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are within factory specifications. With a pristine undercarriage and zero fluid seepage, this atmospheric V8 remains a benchmark for hydraulic steering feedback and mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
