    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-quality 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman S in Carrara White Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and exhibits a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish, protected by a professional ceramic coating. The interior is pristine; the Agate Grey leather remains taut and supple, still retaining its original scent with absolutely no wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with every maintenance milestone performed early at authorized centers. It delivers a tight, responsive driving experience that feels indistinguishable from a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been pampered since day one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
